STEP 30 CHECK_AUTOTRUST example.com
FILE_BEGIN
example.com.	10800	IN	DNSKEY	257 3 5 AwEAAc3Z5DQDJpH4oPdNtC4BUQHk50XMD+dHr4r8psHmivIa83hxR5CRgCtd9sENCW9Ae8OIO19xw9t/RPaEAqQa+OE= ;{id = 55582 (ksk), size = 512b}
